 that the extended Hermite kernel, governing the joint\nprobabilities for the Dyson process, converges to the extended Airy and Sine\nkernels after the appropriate rescalings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2004 21:46:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2004 22:39:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2004 16:36:10 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2005 08:06:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
