operties\nof quantum mechanics based on C_{n} and on R_{n} space are briefly\ninvestigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Mar 2004 21:38:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 24 Jun 2004 16:45:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
